                <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conf. 181.9202/91: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to Officer in Charge in General <persName type="to">Bandholtz</persName>’
                        Absence</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-09-08">September 8,
                            1919</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. [From Polk.] Please rush following message to General Bandholtz: “Do not be
                    drawn into discussion of diplomatic questions with Roumanian officials. Please
                    telegraph immediately object of your trip.” Polk.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Am</hi>[<hi rend="smallcaps">erican</hi>] <hi
                        rend="smallcaps">Mission</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
